1. VM Instance()

  • In Google Cloud Console -> Navigation Menu -> Compute Engine -> Create Instance
    • Machine type : Shared-core, e2-micro
    • Region
    • [ CREATE ]

2. Custom Role

  • In Google Cloud Console -> Navigation Menu -> IAM & Admin -> Roles -> CREATE ROLE
    • TitleInstance_schedule
    • DescriptionCreate on: 2021-10-03
    • IDCustomRolexxx
    • Role launch stageGeneral Availability
    • [ADD PERMISSIONS] , compute.instances.start compute.instances.stop, [ADD]
    • [CREATE]

3. custom role account

  • In Google Cloud Console -> Navigation Menu -> IAM & Admin -> IAM -> [ Include Google-provided role grants ]
  • service-xxxxxxx@compute-system.iam.gserviceaccount.com, [ Edit ]

  • [ ADD ANOTHER ROLE ] -> instance_scheduler -> SAVE

4. Instance schedule

  • VM instances -> INSTANCE SCHEDULES -> [ CREATE SCHEDULE ], , -> [ SUBMIT ]
